description:
This is a special version for Google Chromecast of the Extended version of Dan Brown's book and movie, &quot;The Da Vinci Code&quot;. 

Audio track is in English. English subtitles, only for French and Latin dialog portions, are hard-embedded on screen.

Google Chromecast supports just a limited number of video and audio codecs and container file types. Chromecast still does not handle subtitles, so the English subtitles have been overlayed directly on the video image with this download.

Video: H264 ( 1280 x 528 ) --- Audio: AAC (m4a) stereo 48000

Movie file with embedded subtitles was created using VLC from a 720p YIFY RIP.
